{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.termReturn\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">termReturn</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`return` used outside of `do` blocks creates an implicit block around it\nand thus is equivalent to `pure e`, but helps with avoiding parentheses.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.termReturn","kind":"def","line":340,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.termReturn","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L340-L345"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.termTry\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">termTry</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.termTry","kind":"def","line":338,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.termTry","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L338-L339"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.termFor\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">termFor</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.termFor","kind":"def","line":336,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.termFor","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L336-L337"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.termUnless\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">termUnless</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`unless e do s` is a nicer way to write `if !e do s`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.termUnless","kind":"def","line":333,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.termUnless","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L333-L335"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.do\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">do</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.do","kind":"def","line":325,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.do","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L325-L326"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doNested\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doNested</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doNested","kind":"def","line":322,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doNested","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L322-L323"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doExpr\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doExpr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doExpr","kind":"def","line":318,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doExpr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L318-L321"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doRepeatUntil\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doRepeatUntil</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doRepeatUntil","kind":"def","line":299,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doRepeatUntil","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L299-L300"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doWhile\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doWhile</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doWhile","kind":"def","line":297,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doWhile","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L297-L298"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doRepeat\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doRepeat</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doRepeat","kind":"def","line":295,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doRepeat","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L295-L296"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doDebugAssert\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doDebugAssert</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`debug_assert! cond` panics if `cond` evaluates to `false` and the executing code has been built\nwith debug assertions enabled (see the `debugAssertions` option).\n","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doDebugAssert","kind":"def","line":288,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doDebugAssert","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L288-L293"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doAssert\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doAssert</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`assert! cond` panics if `cond` evaluates to `false`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doAssert","kind":"def","line":283,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doAssert","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L283-L287"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doIdbg\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doIdbg</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"*experimental*\n\n`idbg e` enables live inspection of program state from the editor. When placed in a `do` block,\nit captures all local variables in scope and the expression `e`, then:\n\n- **In the language server**: starts a TCP server on localhost waiting for the running program to\n  connect; the editor will mark this part of the program as \"in progress\" during this wait but that\n  will not block `lake build` of the project.\n- **In the compiled program**: on first execution of the `idbg` call site, connects to the server,\n  receives the expression, compiles and evaluates it using the program's actual runtime values, and\n  sends the `repr` result back.\n\nThe result is displayed as an info diagnostic on the `idbg` keyword. The expression `e` can be\nedited while the program is running - each edit triggers re-elaboration of `e`, a new TCP exchange,\nand an updated result. This makes `idbg` a live REPL for inspecting and experimenting with\nprogram state at a specific point in execution. Only when `idbg` is inserted, moved, or removed does\nthe program need to be recompiled and restarted.\n\n# Known Limitations\n\n* The program will poll the server for up to 10 minutes and needs to be killed manually\n  otherwise.\n* Use of multiple `idbg` at once untested, likely too much overhead from overlapping imports without\n  further changes.\n* `LEAN_PATH` must be properly set up so the compiled program can import its origin module.\n* Untested on Windows and macOS.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doIdbg","kind":"def","line":253,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doIdbg","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L253-L282"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doDbgTrace\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doDbgTrace</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`dbg_trace e` prints `e` (which can be an interpolated string literal) to stderr.\nIt should only be used for debugging.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doDbgTrace","kind":"def","line":247,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doDbgTrace","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L247-L252"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doReturn\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doReturn</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`return e` inside of a `do` block makes the surrounding block evaluate to `pure e`,\nskipping any further statements.\nNote that uses of the `do` keyword in other syntax like in `for _ in _ do`\ndo not constitute a surrounding block in this sense;\nin supported editors, the corresponding `do` keyword of the surrounding block\nis highlighted when hovering over `return`.\n\n`return` not followed by a term starting on the same line is equivalent to `return ()`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doReturn","kind":"def","line":235,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doReturn","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L235-L246"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doContinue\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doContinue</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`continue` skips to the next iteration of the surrounding `for` loop. ","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doContinue","kind":"def","line":233,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doContinue","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L233-L234"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doBreak\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doBreak</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`break` exits the surrounding `for` loop. ","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doBreak","kind":"def","line":231,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doBreak","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L231-L232"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doForward\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doForward</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`do← s` (or ASCII `do<- s`) hands `s` to the enclosing wrapper as a body\nwhose control-flow effects (`return`, `break`, `continue`, `mut`-variable\nreassignment) target the surrounding `do` block, not the body's local monad.\n\nThe syntax is reminiscent of a nested action `(← s)`, but unlike a nested\naction, `s` is not run eagerly in the `do` block context before the wrapping\nfunction is called. The wrapping function decides when to run `s`, and code\nis inserted to forward `s`'s effects to the outer `do` block.\n\nOnly valid as the last argument of a function application that itself appears\nas a statement of an outer `do` block, optionally wrapped in `fun` binders.\nExamples:\n* `f a₁ … aₙ (do← s)`\n* `f a₁ … aₙ (fun b₁ … bₖ => do← s)`\n","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doForward","kind":"def","line":212,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doForward","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L212-L229"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doTry\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doTry</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doTry","kind":"def","line":209,"name":"Lean.Parser.Term.doTry","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Parser/Do.lean#L209-L210"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Parser/Do.html#Lean.Parser.Term.doFinally\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Parser</span>.<span class=\"name\">Term</span>.<span class=\"name\">doFinally</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Parser/Types.html#Lean.Parser.Parser\">Parser</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Par